    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126190/extras/962e90f2c44a51bf2eea2dc44d511062.avif?t=1767634911\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126190/extras_big/962e90f2c44a51bf2eea2dc44d511062.avif?t=1767634911 width=800 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126190/extras/075a447437c39e7b022b2316446ee757.poster.avif?t=1767634911\" width=616 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126190/extras/075a447437c39e7b022b2316446ee757.webm?t=1767634911\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >摆脱神秘的时间循环！坚定不移地踏上一段自我发现之旅，深入调查谜团重重的偏远小镇：懊悔谷。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一天都像是在与自己内心的阴暗艰苦战斗。在旅途中，你将邂逅一群魅力十足的角色，他们每个人都在与自己的复杂情感作斗争。逐渐了解他们之后，你还会发现他们深藏不露的一面。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你能否鼓起勇气揭开时间异常的秘密？又能否发现自己内心的力量，战胜逆境，开创美好的未来？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126190/extras/64260891d3089535d976f7898a285054.poster.avif?t=1767634911\" width=1170 height=683 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126190/extras/64260891d3089535d976f7898a285054.webm?t=1767634911\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以在《懊悔谷》中塑造自己的人格。你可以成为疑虑重重的冷酷独行侠，也可以是个相信直觉、多愁善感的大嘴巴。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论你是选择反映自己的真实人格，还是扮演一个完全不同的人，你的角色都将影响游戏中的对话和互动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你能够以独属于自己的方式推进剧情，同时通过在图表中储存记忆来解锁意图和思维模式。你可以采用奇怪的思维模式进行出乎意料的有趣对话，并体验各种能够改变人格的状态效果，例如在喝醉时变得更外向，或在焦虑时变得格外敏感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你大可尝试不同的回答和时间线，因为时间循环总能让你从头再来，不是吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126190/extras/d28f74c97da6f7849a7e30b3418d23a6.poster.avif?t=1767634911\" width=1170 height=683 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126190/extras/d28f74c97da6f7849a7e30b3418d23a6.webm?t=1767634911\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
